## Current state (detected)
- No automated tests in repo.
- Primary verification is manual in browser.

## Best-practice testing guidance (no-bundler friendly)

### Manual smoke checklist (storefront)
- Catalog loads:
  - First load shows skeleton then products
  - Subsequent load uses cache then refreshes in background
- Filters:
  - Search, category, condition, sort work together
  - Out-of-stock items sort to the end and show “Indisponível”
- Product modal:
  - Options switching updates price/image and availability correctly
  - Out-of-stock blocks “Eu Quero”
- Cart:
  - Add/remove/quantity updates total and badge
  - Finalize opens WhatsApp message and posts order in background
- Compare:
  - Add up to 3, toast appears, comparison table renders

### Manual smoke checklist (dashboard)
- Login gate:
  - Logged-out redirects to `dashboard/index.html`
  - Logged-in redirects to `dashboard/dashboard.html`
- Data load:
  - Orders + products load from Apps Script
  - KPIs and charts render without console errors
- Status change:
  - Changing status updates sheet and refreshes dashboard
  - Stock updates apply when status becomes `Fechado`
- Stock management:
  - Editing `estoque` / `estoque_minimo` enables Save, syncs to sheet, then hides Save

### Suggested future automation (optional)
If/when you introduce tooling, consider:
- Playwright “smoke” suite hitting `http://localhost:<port>/` (requires a static server)
- A small contract test script validating Apps Script responses (shape + required fields)
